Why , Pete , what is it ? Are you sick ? '' she cried , her glance encompassing the half set table . 
No , ma'am oh , no , ma'am ! '' The old man stumbled forward and began to arrange the knives and forks . 
It's just a pesky pain beggin' yer pardon in my side . 
'' Billy frowned and shook her head . 
