I'd have gone down into the kitchen myself if I'd suspected what was going on . 
'' Arkwright raised his eyebrows . 
Perhaps it's well you didn't if Bertram's picture of what he found there when he went down is a true one . 
Mrs. Henshaw acknowledges that even the cat sought refuge under the stove . 
