Well , I expect I am , and '' Oh , Cyril ! '' The door had opened , and Marie was in the room . 
If she gave a start of surprise at her husband's unaccustomed attitude , she quickly controlled herself . 
Julia said you wanted me . 
Before Mrs. Henshaw could answer , Cyril , who had got to his feet , turned sharply . 
Is it who ? '' he demanded . 
Oh ! Oh , Mr. Henshaw , '' stammered the girl . 
