Dot and Dimple , indeed ! '' he went on wrathfully . 
We'll name those boys to day , Marie , to day ! Not once again will I let the sun go down on a Dot and a Dimple under my roof . 
'' Marie turned with a quick little cry of happiness . 
Great Scott ! '' And , entirely forgetting what he had come to the nursery for , Cyril strode from the room . 
Ah goo spggggh ! '' commented baby from the middle of the floor . 
It was on a very windy March day that Bertram Henshaw's son , Bertram , Jr . 
, arrived at the Strata . 
Even when the days had become weeks , and Bertram , Jr . 
